  "body": "QBFT uses the same validator management logic that IBFT2 and IBFT use and allows for a lot of code reuse. This will make it possible for bft based consensus mechanism to use it's own specific mechanism to manage validators i.e. determining what the validators are and the mechanism to add and remove them.\n\nThis is needed so that QBFT can move using transaction based validator management using smart contracts.\n\nRequirements:\n- Create a common interface for retrieving validators with optional support for voting\n- Move existing code to use the common interface",
